SLS Camera Firmware packaging
Copyright (c) 2026 SLS Camera contributors

The scripts and documentation in this repository are provided for building
appliance images for the SLS Camera project.

Application source code is maintained in the separate "sls-camera" repository
and remains under that project's license terms.

Third-party packages (Ubuntu, PyPI, MediaPipe models, etc.) retain their own
licenses. Do not redistribute non-redistributable firmware (e.g. Microsoft
Kinect UAC audio firmware) via this repository.
